(1, '40989', 'Driver Sales Representative', 'Con-way Freight', 3.2, 3.2, 2.7, 3.4, 3, 2.9, 65, '* Operate tractor-trailer combination, including doubles (and triples, where applicable)<br><br>\r\n* Perform daily pre-trip and safety inspections on equipment<br><br>\r\n* Hook/Unhook trailer and converter dollies to/from a tractor and/or trailer<br><br>\r\n * Demonstrate internal and external customer service, asking for additional business to provide new sales leads for potential new opportunities<br><br>\r\n* Load and unload freight as required<br><br>\r\n* Complete all necessary paperwork and maintain records<br><br>\r\n* Work in adverse weather conditions<br><br>\r\n* Collect and document receipt of cash and checks on shipment-collect and cash-on-delivery shipments<br><br>\r\n* Safely operates tractor-trailer equipment or straight trucks as assigned\r\n<br><br>', '* Class A Commercial driver’s license with hazardous and doubles/triples endorsements issued by this state <br><br>\r\n* Ability to operate a fork lift, including changing and using various accessories<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated truck driving experience with either straight truck or tractor/trailer combination necessary with exemplary driving record<br><br>\r\n* Can read, write, communicate, and comprehend the English language sufficiently to perform the various tasks of the job<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated ability to maintain good attendance<br><br>\r\n* 21 years of age or older\r\n\r\n', '4967', 16, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/40989/con-way-freight-squarelogo-1446489252711.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Con-way-Freight-RVW7574520.htm'),
(2, '35565', 'PHE Supervisor', 'Oxfam', 3.8, 4.2, 3.1, 3.1, 3.3, 3.7, 77, '* Maintains staff by recruiting, selecting, orienting, and training employees; developing personal growth opportunities. <br><br>\r\n* Accomplishes staff job results by coaching, counseling, and disciplining employees; planning, monitoring, and appraising job results; conducting training; implementing enforcing systems, policies, and procedures. <br><br>\r\n* Maintains safe and healthy work environment by establishing and enforcing organization standards; adhering to legal regulations.<br><br>\r\n* Completes operations by developing schedules; assigning and monitoring work; gathering resources; implementing productivity standards; resolving operations problems; maintaining reference manuals; implementing new procedures.<br><br>\r\n* Controls expenses by gathering and submitting budget information; scheduling expenditures; monitoring variances; implementing corrective actions. <br><br>\r\n* Provides quality service by enforcing quality and customer service standards.\r\n* Maintains professional and technical knowledge by attending educational workshops; reviewing professional publications. <br><br>\r\n* Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed.\r\n', '* Tracking Budget Expenses <br><br>\r\n* Supervision, Quality Management <br><br>\r\n* Safety Management<br><br>\r\n* Staffing<br><br>\r\n* Delegation<br><br>\r\n* Performance Management<br><br>\r\n* Organization<br><br>\r\n* Foster Teamwork<br><br>\r\n* Self-Development<br><br>\r\n* Giving Feedback<br><br>', '4967', 25, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/35565/oxfam-squarelogo-1413967664927.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Oxfam-RVW9898675.htm'),
(4, '460850', 'Public Health Assistant', 'IOM', 3.4, 3.6, 3.1, 3.6, 3.1, 3.3, 78, '     Provides assistance to special education teachers; performs tasks related to the physical and instructional needs of students with disabilities in a special educational setting; and assists with implementation of classroom programs and activities.', '* Any combination of education and experience equivalent to graduation from high school, plus one year of progressively more responsible experience working with children. <br><br>\r\n* Can demonstrate basic knowledge of child growth and development, group interaction, health, safety, and first-aid methods <br><br> \r\n* sensitivity to the ways in which physical and intellectual disabilities affect the behavior of children; ability to establish warm and supportive relationships with children on both a group and individual basis <br><br>\r\n* ability to assist with providing a wide variety of stimulating experiences for children to meet their individual, intellectual, and emotional needs <br><br>\r\n* ability to assist teacher with use and adaptation of a range of instructional techniques and to participate in the monitoring and control of a wide range of behaviors. May be required to lift wheelchairs and related equipment and/or to assist another person with transferring, lifting, or positioning students<br><br>\r\n* may be trained in the use of a particular type of equipment or a specialized skill, such as ability to communicate with children with special disability (e.g., deaf/blind and nonverbal)<br><br>\r\n* Some positions may require physical strength, agility, and dexterity to restrain students whose behavior is disruptive or dangerous to self or other students.', '4967', 12, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/460850/iom-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-IOM-RVW2869248.htm'),
(5, '40417', 'Employee', 'Bank Danamon Indonesia', 3.2, 3, 2.9, 2.9, 3.4, 3.4, 62, '  Program Management Trainee (MT) dirancang untuk menyiapkan future leaders Tunas Finance melalui pengembangan karir jalur cepat (fast track).', '* Pendidikan min. S1 segala jurusan dari Universitas terkemuka<br><br>\r\n* IPK minimum 3,00<br><br>\r\n* Usia maksimum 25 Tahun<br><br>\r\n* Mampu berbahasa Inggris (lisan dan tulisan)<br><br>\r\n* Antusias, kreatif, berorientasi pada hasil, dan percaya diri<br><br>\r\n* Memiliki pengalaman organisasi<br><br>\r\n* Mahir dalam menggunakan Microsoft Office<br><br>\r\n* Belum menikah & bersedia untuk tidak menikah selama masa pendidikan berlangsung<br><br>\r\n* Bersedia penempatan di seluruh kantor MTF di Indonesia<br><br>\r\n* Bersedia untuk menjalani ikatan dinas dalam waktu yang ditentukan<br><br>\r\n', '4967', 23, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/40417/bank-danamon-indonesia-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Bank-Danamon-Indonesia-RVW2636266.htm'),
(8, '14903', 'Peace Corps Volunteer', 'Peace Corps', 4.1, 4.5, 3.5, 3, 3.8, 3.7, 93, '   Four Peace Corps Response Volunteers are needed to serve as Community Health Outreach Volunteers for the Ministry of Health, Last Mile Health (LMH), or Partners in Health (PIH). Peace Corps Liberia is launching a new health project, which will support the new National Community Health Services Plan. Volunteers will work within the new Community Health system to improve maternal and child health through capacity building of service providers and direct household-level interventions.', '* RPCV who served in a Health Project.<br><br>\r\n* Experience in at least one of the following public health areas during PC service or through other professional work in a developing country: maternal health, infant and young child health or nutrition, household WASH, malaria control, household-level health outreach, TB/HIV.<br><br>\r\n* Project management experience and demonstrated skills.', '4968', 24, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/14903/peace-corps-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Peace-Corps-RVW8857294.htm'),
(9, '921624', 'Online Marketing Consultant', 'Livit', 4.8, 4.9, 4.7, 4, 4.4, 4.8, 100, '   This position is responsible for the identification, design and development of enhancements for My Verizon and other self service functions. Project lead identifies enhancements, outlines user experience, documents business requirements, communicates with stakeholders and follows up with analysis and reporting. The position requires that they partner with IT to create mutually agreed upon approaches for implementation and ensuring flawless execution. They lead multiple critical projects simultaneously while ensuring on time delivery of all items associated with the project. The area of focus for this position will be on enhancing the various merchandising pods throughout the My Verizon digital properties to drive acquisition, revenue and customer loyalty', '* Bachelor’s degree or four or more years of work experience.<br><br>\r\n* Four or more years of relevant work experience.<br><br>\r\n* Four or more years marketing experience in ecommerce marketing, website management or website merchandising<br><br>\r\n* Three or more years of experience analyzing data, preparing reports and recommendations<br><br>\r\n* Strong analytical and technical skills.<br><br>\r\n* Experienced in evaluating creative and recommending improvements to improve results.<br><br>\r\n* High computer literacy, with the ability to learn new systems and tools quickly.<br><br>\r\n* Advanced knowledge of Microsoft Excel, Word and PowerPoint required for data manipulation and presentations.<br><br>\r\n* Ability to work independently and prioritize work assignments, based on changing business needs.<br><br>\r\n* Excellent verbal and written communication, organization and interpersonal skills', '4968', 7, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/921624/livit-squarelogo-1416818226048.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Livit-RVW9524886.htm'),
(12, '2989', 'Agronomist', 'Stanford University', 4.2, 4.2, 3.6, 3.6, 4, 3.8, 88, '   The Intern will effectively employ all available resources and technology in order to provide producer customers with the excellence of agronomic information and service generated by Servi-Tech, Inc.', '*  The Intern is attending an agricultural college working on a Bachelor of Science degree.<br><br>\r\n* Good communication, public relations skills, and basic computer functions skills are required.', '4968', 8, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/2989/stanford-university-squarelogo-1431968559974.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Stanford-University-RVW9482978.htm'),
(13, '32408', 'Recruiting Coordinator', 'Anonymous Content', 3.1, 3.1, 2.8, 2.9, 3, 3.1, 56, 'Coordinate end-to-end recruitment process.', 'Graduated with a Bachelor degree from all major. At least 2 years of working experience in the related fields is required, preferrably from top 10 headhunter company.', '4968', 10, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/32408/anonymous-content-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Anonymous-Content-RVW5494536.htm'),
(14, '3774', 'Employee', 'Club Med', 3.6, 4.1, 3.1, 2.8, 3.7, 2.9, 72, '* Ensuring the maintenance and repairing sanitary facilities<br><br>\r\n* Regularly carrying out preventive maintenance measures also in other fields (electricity, joiner’s jobs)<br><br>\r\n* Implementing and respecting hygiene and safety procedures<br><br>\r\n* Ensure all the “cold” equipment in the resort functions properly, efficiently and safely<br><br>\r\n* Deal with all the complaints concerning the service, efficiently and reactively\r\n', '* Convenient to communicate in English<br><br>\r\n* Can repair all equipment that need to repair, focusing on clean, lasting and safe outcome<br><br>\r\n* Work experience in the field preferred<br><br>\r\n* Ability to work long hours and work pressure<br><br>\r\n* Willing to travel alone\r\n', '4968', 23, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3774/club-med-squarelogo-1432805372123.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Club-Med-RVW6675040.htm'),
(15, '323167', 'Instructional Designer', 'Praxis Interactive Technologies', 1.9, 2.5, 1.7, 1.8, 2, 2.1, 24, '   Instructional Designer will provide direction and coordination in designing, developing, and delivering online, mobile, paper, or live and technology-enhanced instructional materials for public health professionals and key vulnerable populations. This position is a temporary, as needed position. ', '* BA with 3 years instructional/educational technology experience, including designing, developing, and managing higher education (and/or corporate) technology-based instruction projects and programs required<br><br>\r\n* Advanced degree in instructional design or instructional/educational technology field and 5 years relevant experience preferred<br><br>\r\n* Self-motivated, organized, and detail-oriented team player who is capable of participating in collaborative instructional development processes and activities, is able to work independently, and has strong intellectual and analytical skills<br><br>\r\n* Extensive knowledge of current and emerging instructional technologies<br><br>\r\n* Experience in Articulate Storyline, SnagIt, and/or Camtasia preferred\r\nProven ability to continually adapt and learn new procedures and software programs<br><br>\r\n* Strong knowledge of pedagogical issues related to online teaching and learning, particularly adult and mastery learning\r\nAbility to work collaboratively within an academic community<br><br>\r\n* Experience with training, staff development, and teaching<br><br>\r\n* Ability to interpret client needs\r\nCommitment to customer service<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated written, presentation, and interpersonal communications skills<br><br>\r\n* Effective negotiation and diplomacy skills<br><br>\r\n* Ability to anticipate and solve problems<br><br>\r\n* Ability to manage and meet deadlines ', '4968', 5, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/323167/praxis-interactive-technologies-squarelogo-1412356985819.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Praxis-Interactive-Technologies-RVW6646422.htm'),
(16, '380096', 'Online English Teacher', 'EnglishTown', 2.1, 2.5, 2.1, 2.2, 2.3, 3.1, 27, '* Deliver 30 minutes GVE Live Interactive Video Lessons - Internet video interaction with students from grades 1 to grade 9 using ZOOM (video conferencing tool) to enhance English communication abilities both listening and speaking<br><br>\r\n* Provide constructive feedback to students to help them improve their speaking skills<br><br>\r\n* Create a safe, positive, respectful and supportive online environment, to help GVE Chinese students successfully complete learning goals of each lesson and progress to a higher level of English communication proficiency<br><br>\r\n* Work flexible hours coordinated with GVE’s Online Lesson Schedule<br><br>\r\n', '* Keeping student records and profile cards up to date<br><br>\r\n* Participating in your performance evaluation plan<br><br>\r\n* Integrating learning technology into teaching programs<br><br>\r\n* Maintaining center resource materials ', '4968', 8, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/380096/englishtown-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-EnglishTown-RVW7458093.htm'),
(17, '34785', 'Store Keeper', 'Heifer International', 3.6, 3.7, 3.4, 3.2, 3.4, 3.7, 72, 'Pengalaman yang dibutuhkan:\r\nShopkeeper/SPG/SPB: 1 tahun', '* Pria/ Wanita <br><br>\r\n* Pendidikan min. SMA/ Sederajat<br><br>\r\n* Memiliki pengalaman sebagai shop keeper/penjaga toko/SPG/SPB<br><br>\r\n* Dapat bekerja dalam tim, jujur, dan bertanggung jawab<br><br>\r\n* Memiliki kemampuan dalam berkomunikasi dengan pembeli, supel, rewel<br><br>\r\n* Dapat mengoperasikan Microsoft Word dan Microsoft Excel<br><br>', '4968', 27, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/34785/heifer-international-squarelogo-1482433946377.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Heifer-International-RVW6051297.htm'),
(18, '484593', 'Software Engineer', 'Mitrais', 3.7, 3.8, 3.2, 3.6, 3.5, 3.9, 85, '   You will work on leading edge projects often with start-up companies developing exciting new concepts for the international marketplace. You can choose to be based in either our Bali, Bandung, or Yogyakarta offices.', '* Excellent English communication skills<br><br>\r\n* Proficient with developing, deploying, customizing and integrating Microsoft Dynamics CRM<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated proficiency in installing and deploying CRM Organizations<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated proficiency in customizing and creating CRM entities<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated proficiency in understanding and implementing business workflows and processes<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated proficiency in using either the CRM SDK or plugin platforms<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated proficiency with Microsoft .NET 3.5+ development using C#<br><br>\r\n* Experience with source control management systems and continuous integration/deployment environments<br><br>\r\n* Internally motivated, able to work proficiently both independently and in a team environment<br><br>\r\n* Proven communication skills with both internal team members and external business stakeholders<br><br>\r\n* Strong initiative to find ways to improve solutions, systems, and processes<br><br>\r\n* Relevant Degree (Associate Degree and/or Bachelor Degree)\r\n', '4968', 18, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/484593/mitrais-squarelogo-1424683367189.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Mitrais-RVW14361785.htm'),
(19, '929060', 'Employee', 'Hotel Shangri-La', 2.2, 2.3, 2, 2.3, 2.2, 2, 23, 'Good benefits, generous bonuses, strong brand name on CV, fast pace at the work place, great career exposure.', '* Effective bilingual in English & Malay<br><br>\r\n* Minimum SPM & Minimum 2 years in the similar capacity<br><br>\r\n* Computer literate<br><br>\r\n* Customer orientation, Enthusiasm, Team builder, Initiative, Self starter<br><br>\r\n* Good Interpersonal skills<br><br>\r\n* Committed to customer values<br><br>\r\n* Due to work pass restriction only Malaysian can apply\r\n', '4968', 23, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/929060/hotel-shangri-la-squarelogo-1466075112892.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Hotel-Shangri-La-RVW10071304.htm'),
(24, '4138', 'Internship', 'Accenture', 3.7, 3.8, 3.2, 3.4, 3.7, 3.2, 82, '   Interns at Accenture have the opportunity to work alongside our top performing Consultants, gaining exposure to how business processes work and interact. As a member of a project team you will gain exposure to skills such as process re-engineering, technology, system implementation and organizational change.   \r\n   As an Intern, you will be engaged to work for a 2 to 6-month placement. You will be provided with orientation and on-project learning, before being placed into a live project team. You will gain a true understanding and experience of what a career in Consulting means and what it is like to be an Accenture Consultant.', '* Passion for consulting<br><br>\r\n* Characteristics of a future leader<br><br>\r\n* Good communication and interpersonal skills<br><br>\r\n* Excellent verbal and written English language skills', '4970', 23, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/4138/accenture-squarelogo-1484658508051.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Accenture-RVW14380932.htm'),
(25, '8450', 'Intern', 'PwC', 3.7, 3.8, 3.4, 3.3, 4, 2.9, 80, '   You will participate in training designed to develop your skills. There are workshops and online trainings mostly at the beginning of the learning experience. Together with coaching and on-the-job experience it makes an important part of your development at PwC. Coaching shall help you to achieve higher performance and shape your future career with purpose.', '* Learning About the Business<br><br>\r\n* Understanding Business Borrowing Needs<br><br>\r\n* Assessing the Business and Management<br><br>\r\n* Financial Statement analysis<br><br>\r\n* Credit Facilities, Loan Support, and Pricing<br><br>\r\n* Effective Communications and Credit Write-ups<br><br>', '4970', 23, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/8450/pwc-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-PwC-RVW14483507.htm'),
(26, '354', 'Sales Specialist', 'IBM', 3.4, 3.4, 2.9, 3.1, 3.4, 3.6, 63, '   Do you want to work with the most exciting technology startups and disruptors in the industry? Do you have the drive and techno-functional background necessary to take IBM to the next level? Are you the new IBM?\r\nIBM is currently in pursuit of senior sales leaders that will be responsible for day to day activities associated with managing and developing sales accounts for our consulting services (management consulting as well as outsourcing), Systems (Software & Hardware), Cloud, Analytics, Mobile, Social, Security, Watson, etc.\r\nActivities would include managing the sales pipeline, finding new opportunities, and the qualification of those opportunities to establish a client base.', '* 5+ years direct enterprise software selling experience; a top producer<br><br>\r\n* 3-5 years of experience managing software sales teams<br><br>\r\n* Expertise in leading and coordinating the development of complex proposals<br><br>\r\n* Demonstrated ability to think strategically and act decisively to create the future<br><br>\r\n* Significant expertise in customer and market-facing software sales positions as both individual contributor and sales leader<br><br>\r\n* Data-centric and proven analytical skills including complex modelling and forecasting. Proven ability to synthesize market information to translate data into knowledge to better inform action.<br><br>\r\n*  Ability to build deep trust with internal teammates and end customer executives<br><br>\r\n*  Innovation and creativity, with the ability to devise best practices.<br><br>\r\n*  Technical acumen to interface with technologists, understand complex concepts and translate in a way that businesses stakeholders can understand<br><br>\r\n*  Experienced in using structured sales methodologies for selling to large accounts<br><br>\r\n*  Professional maturity to lead the way and manage skillfully through long sales cycles', '4970', 16, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/354/ibm-squarelogo-1491487414453.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-IBM-RVW14465393.htm'),
(27, '2784', 'Assistant', 'EY', 3.7, 3.8, 3.4, 3.3, 4, 2.9, 81, '   As part of our business development team, you’ll build strategic relationships with executives from leading organizations. You will specifically focus on two market segments - Financial Services Organization (FSO) and Government Public Sector (GPS). Apart from that, you will also assist EY Indonesia in developing Good Governance practice. By understanding their business issues and imperatives and collaborating with other teams, you’ll broaden your experience. Collaborating with other teams, you will help to identify and shape the solutions to client issues. Backed by the resources of a global organization, you’ll gain experiences and foster relationships that will support your long-term success.\r\nThe Business Development Assistant/Associate Director works with the Client Service Partners (CSPs), Business Development Leader (BDL) and client account teams to proactively develop and execute on markets strategy to maximize growth and achieve targeted results.', '* Bachelor''s degree or equivalent experienceA Bachelor degree with relevant post graduate/professional qualification is desirable<br><br>\r\n*  At least 10 years of relevant work experience, equivalent to 6-8 years relevant work experience when having the appropriate Graduate Degree (Master) in business development, sales management and/or the sales process in Banking, Insurance or Financial Services Industry<br><br>\r\n*  Proven revenue generating track record through business development, sales, and bidding management.<br><br>\r\n*   Possess good network and strong knowledge of the target markets will be advantageous<br><br>\r\n*  Good business acumen with excellent sales and negotiation skills<br><br>\r\n*  Strong project and people management experience, good organizational skills and attention to detail<br><br>\r\n*  Excellent written, oral, presentation and facilitation skills<br><br>\r\n*  Executive presence, able to quickly establish personal credibility and demonstrate expertise<br><br>\r\n*  Strong proven analytical, conceptual and strategic skills; able to foresee the market potential and develop strategies to grow the business<br><br>\r\n*  Highly motivated, persistent, results driven attitude and able to overcome barriers and get results through people', '4970', 27, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/2784/ey-squarelogo-1434645705166.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-EY-RVW14348668.htm'),
(28, '3513', 'Assistant Finance Manager', 'Unilever', 3.8, 4.1, 3.4, 3.5, 3.5, 3.6, 82, '  The role of the Ben & Jerry’s Associate Finance Manager (AFM) is to provide decision support and financial insight to help the Ben & Jerry’s team deliver profitable growth and meet its annual targets in a manner consistent with the 3-part mission and linked prosperity model. The AFM will play an active role in the development of financial and brand investment plans, will monitor performance against objectives, and will evaluate social mission opportunities.', '* Bachelor’s Degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field; MBA or CPA strongly preferred<br><br>\r\n*  Minimum of four years of related financial planning and analysis experience with increasing responsibility and control<br><br>\r\n*  Prior work experience in Brand, Supply Chain, Customer Development (Sales), Audit, Accounting, Financial Reporting, or Financial Planning is preferred<br><br>\r\n*  An enterprising and inquisitive nature that can find solutions to complex problems<br><br>\r\n*  Experience creating and implementing process improvement solutions<br><br>\r\n*  Excellent verbal and written communication skills to clearly communicate results and implications of analysis in both verbal and written forms<br><br>\r\n*  Experience communicating effectively with all levels leadership, and experience communicating with all levels of financial acumen<br><br>\r\n*  Enjoy working in a collaborative team environment<br><br>\r\n*  Have proficiency in the following systems: BI, Hyperion, Excel, SAP, Word, and PowerPoint.', '4970', 25, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3513/unilever-squarelogo-1441224713183.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Unilever-RVW14192062.htm'),
(29, '3472', 'Human Resources Specialist', 'Ericsson-Worldwide', 3.6, 3.8, 2.9, 3.5, 3.3, 3.8, 73, 'Responsibilities and Tasks:<br><br>\r\n*  Maintains employee and organization information through Personnel Administration and Organization Management in HRIS (SAP-HR)<br><br>\r\n*  Handles bulk requests related to personnel administration and reorganization.<br><br>\r\n*  Handles HRIS concerns and resolves cases and issues<br><br>\r\n*  Ensures the accuracy of the tasks and processes being performed in the HRIS<br><br>\r\n*  Makes the initiative for escalating issues to the relevant parties and demanding improvements of tools, routines and processes', '* Bachelor degree, preferably within HR or relevant experience within required area<br><br>\r\n*  Extensive experience using SAP HRMS/HRIS doing support/ issue resolution and large ticket volume.<br><br>\r\n*  Presentation and communication skills<br><br>\r\n*  Proactive, service oriented mind-set', '4970', 10, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3472/ericsson-worldwide-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Ericsson-Worldwide-RVW11194695.htm'),
(30, '588', 'IT Analyst', 'Schlumberger', 3.4, 3.4, 2.9, 3.7, 3.5, 2.6, 67, '  We need graduates and experienced people with a range of technical expertise to fill a variety of roles, such as service desk analyst, on-site support analyst, application developer, IT security specialist, and project manager. We expect you to hold a PhD, master''s or bachelor''s in an IT–related subject, or be an IT engineer or IT professional.', '* Bachelor’s of science degree in mathematics or natural science (e.g. Geology, Physics, Computer Science, Geophysics).<br><br>\r\n*  Fluency in written and spoken English.\r\n', '4970', 18, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/588/schlumberger-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Schlumberger-RVW14497530.htm'),
(31, '40419', 'Assistant Manager', 'Bank Mandiri', 3.2, 3.4, 3.4, 3.4, 3.5, 2.7, 72, 'BANK MANDIRI (Assistant Relationship Manager)\r\n<br>\r\nWUJUDKAN KARIRMU BERSAMA BANK MANDIRI', '   Bagi Anda yang memiliki spirit dan motivasi tinggi Bank Mandiri memberikan kesempatan untuk berkarir sebagai Assistant Relationship Manager dengan kualifikasi sebagai berikut :<br><br>\r\n*  Pria dan Wanita<br><br>\r\n*   Usia maks. 24.00 tahun bagi yang belum memiliki pengalaman bekerja dan maks. 26.00 tahun bagi yang telah memiliki pengalaman bekerja di bidang Perbankan bagian kredit<br><br>\r\n*  Pendidikan min. S1 dengan IPK min. 2.75<br><br>\r\n*  Universitas Terakreditasi minimal A<br><br>\r\n*  Berpenampilan Menarik<br><br>\r\n*  Tinggi Badan Wanita min. 155 dan Pria min. 165 dengan berat badan Proporsional<br><br>\r\n*  Penguasaan Komputer khususnya Microsoft Office (Word Excel dan Powerpoint) adalah wajib bagi kandidat<br><br>\r\n*  Memiliki kemampuan komunikasi dan kecerdasan serta potensi diri yang baik untuk tumbuh dan berkembang bersama Bank Mandiri', '4970', 27, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/40419/bank-mandiri-squarelogo-1400178763868.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Bank-Mandiri-RVW11091407.htm'),
(32, '393603', 'Engineer', 'XL Axiata', 3.4, 3.1, 2.8, 3.3, 2.7, 3.5, 68, '* Ensure the implementation & conformance of this procedure<br><br>\r\n* Review lifting plan develop by respective Subcon competent lifting engineer<br><br>\r\n* Responsible for lifting equipment selection, procurement and ensure all lifting equipment meets the required standards.<br><br>\r\n* Organise the maintenance & certification of lifting equipment<br><br>\r\n* Ensure safety critical elements are maintained<br><br>\r\n* To establish lifting plan or JSA and risk assessment<br><br>\r\n', '* Minimum S1 majoring in Electrical Engineering, Computer Science, Information System.<br><br>\r\n* The candidate with prior experience in Service Oriented Architecture (SOA) is preferred.<br><br>\r\n*  Minimum 1 year of experience in the design and development of web and mobile applications on web portals, frameworks and mobile application development platforms (IBM, Oracle, SAP, Kony, Phone gap, Appccelerator, Groory on Grails or any similar.<br><br>\r\n*  Have deep experience of building mobile applications is preferred.<br><br>\r\n*  Possess related certification in industry recognized integration.<br><br>\r\n*  Epertise with HTML5, CSS3, Javascript, PHP, Python, XML/XSLT, XPATH, XML Schema, WSDL, SQL, J2EE (Java Web Service), Java, JMS, SOAP, REST, JQuery Mobile, Dojo Mobile, Eclipse, Netbeans, Node.js.<br><br>\r\n*  Strong knowledge of building native applications on IOS using Objective-C and XCODE and on Androin using Java/Android SDK. Also of building hybrid mobile applications.<br><br>\r\n*  The candidate with additional experience on Blackberry and Windows mobile application is preferred.<br><br>\r\n*  Strong knowledge on mobile UI/UX design interface using editors like Eclipse, IntelliJ, ForeUI etc and CMS like Joomla, Drupal, etc.<br><br>\r\n*  Knowledge on building MBaaS servces based on programming languages like JMS, Java, PHP etc. Exposing as Webservice or JSON/REST.<br><br>\r\n*  Previous experience in MADP from IBM, Kony, Pegasus, Phonegap, Xamarin etc.<br><br>\r\n*  Strong knowledge of Database Management (SQL Server and Oracle) and different Unix flavours. The candidate with prior experience in implementing applications on cloud is preferred.<br><br>\r\n*  Strong knowledge of network elements like firewalls, switches, GGSN, DMZ etc and of middleware servuces integration is preferred.\r\n', '4970', 9, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/393603/xl-axiata-squarelogo-1423835832542.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-XL-Axiata-RVW11689948.htm'),
(33, '2763', 'Assistant Manager', 'Deloitte', 3.7, 3.8, 3.4, 3.5, 3.9, 3, 82, '   At Deloitte, we offer a unique and exceptional career experience to inspire and empower talents like you to make an impact that matters for our clients, people and society. Whatever your aspirations, Deloitte offers you unrivalled opportunities to realise your full potential. We are always looking for people with the relentless energy to push themselves further, and to find new avenues and unique ways to reach our shared goals.', '* Good Degree in Accountancy or Business from reputable Universities; or international professional accounting qualification.<br><br>\r\n*  Manager - Registered Certified Public Accountant (CPA) with Myanmar Accountancy Council or Part 3 ACCA with audit experience.<br><br>\r\n*  Assistant manager – Registered CPA or Part 2 ACCA with audit experience<br><br>\r\n*  If ACCA qualified, willingness to study and convert to CPA qualification', '4970', 27, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/2763/deloitte-squarelogo-1481880537463.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Deloitte-RVW14475530.htm'),
(34, '9304', 'Marketing', 'Huawei Technologies', 3.1, 2.6, 2.6, 3.2, 3.1, 2.2, 54, '   Undertake customer communication on SOLAR topic, dialog on SOLAR development and transformation tendency, collect customer requirement, discover market opportunities\r\nIn charge of SOLAR market analysis, track and analyze operators’ transformation strategy and tempo on SOLAR service innovation, new business model, new payment model, draw Huawei on SOLAR solution planning\r\nUndertake Solar product planning, requirement management and definition of solution roadmap\r\nComprehend and analyze customer value, eco-system development, competitor product planning and market status, Huawei market status and product compliance/patent holdings, implement the strategy defined by Standards Strategy Committee, and lead industry going on healthy development and ensure Huawei’s commercial interest.', '* 5 years experience designing commercial/utility PV systems in USA/5 years PV industry experience<br><br>\r\n*  Engineering/Construction background/4 year degree<br><br>\r\n*  Previous employers large PV EPC’s, inverter manufactures<br><br>\r\n*  Will work closely with sales, provide sales support, work directly with customers to solve and analyze PV needs.<br><br>\r\n*  Will give technical presentations to prospectus customers with sales<br><br>\r\n*  Must be willing to travel weekly', '4970', 11, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/9304/huawei-technologies-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Huawei-Technologies-RVW12835490.htm'),
(35, '3494', 'Solutions Manager', 'Nokia', 3.8, 3.9, 3.3, 3.5, 3.4, 4, 80, '* Understand Care Services requirements in customer tenders (Request for Proposals i.e. RFPs) and define Services scope.<br><br>\r\n*  Prepare Care Services sales proposal as response to customer tenders.<br><br>\r\n*  Initiates service kick off & interfaces with Market Service Solution Manager, Renewal Lead, Account Manager etc.<br><br>\r\n*  Define and document technical customer solution, respond to technical sections of tenders, and prepare costing/pricing.<br><br>\r\n*  Develop key contact and relationship with the Global Services Care Business unit and Services Sales/Solution managers in various regions.<br><br>\r\n*  Provide Sales Support to Regional Solution Managers and Customer Teams as member of Global Sales Support (GSS).<br><br>\r\n*  Provide standard solutions and offer material (Statement of Compliance, Services Costing, Standard Pricing, and Service Description).<br><br>\r\n*  Support Sales team to create win plans and deal strategies for key sales opportunities.<br><br>\r\n*  Support CBT/CT with value based selling guidelines and strong value argumentation for the proposed solution.<br><br>\r\n*  Proactively develop, customize and industrialize market specific solutions and costing.<br><br>\r\n*  Interlock with Services CT, Global Services Portfolio sales and Market Services BL heads.<br><br>\r\n*  Build competitive Benchmarking of the solution along with cost benchmarking and risk/mitigation plan.<br><br>\r\n*  Create/capture/consolidate new competence and experiences, best practices, lessons learned for capability development.<br><br>\r\n*  Service strategy & updating services bid directive.<br><br>\r\n*  Responsible and accountable for quality review of the services deliverables.<br><br>\r\n*  Key member for all reviews.<br><br>\r\n*  Ensure the concept of Smart Tendering during bids.<br><br>\r\n*  A source of expertise for others in own product/sales area. Understanding 