(40, '7839', 'Warehouse Analyst', 'Astra International', 3.9, 4.5, 3.3, 3.7, 3.4, 3.7, 100, 'Kami sedang mencari staf kasir di bagian Corporate Treasury PT. Astra International Head office <br><br>\r\n*  Penempatan :<br><br>\r\nPT Astra International Tbk – Head Office\r\nJl.  Gaya Motor Raya No. 8, Sunter II, Jakarta Utara', '* Lulusan Diploma 3, jurusan accounting dan finance lebih diutamakan<br><br>\r\n* Jujur, pintar, dan memiliki keinginan untuk belajar', '4970', 3, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/7839/astra-international-squarelogo-1424263652389.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Astra-International-RVW11435861.htm'),
(41, '446637', 'Research and Development Staff', 'BINUS University', 3.6, 3.7, 3.3, 3.1, 3.3, 3.5, 78, 'A development assistant offers administrative support to an organization''s development office, which brings in money and resources from donors to sustain growth. Development assistants handle a variety of tasks related to institutional and individual giving. Much of the day''s work is spent managing relationships with current and prospective donors, bolstering membership and researching ways to bring in additional funds. This is a crucial role in many non-profit and educational groups that depend on fundraising for survival. ', '* Max. 27 years old.<br><br>\r\n* Bachelor degree of Chemistry with Min. GPA 3.00<br><br>\r\n*  Fresh graduated\r\n', '4970', 17, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/446637/binus-university-squarelogo-1424336956185.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-BINUS-University-RVW13070946.htm'),
(42, '3363', 'Marketing Communications', 'Samsung Electronics', 3.2, 2.7, 2.6, 3.6, 3, 2.6, 56, '• Develop and execute the Product Strategy for the assigned categories.<br><br>\r\n• Delivery of top-line P&L measures of sales volume, revenue and market shares for the assigned categories.<br><br>\r\n• Ensure a market-relevant Product Portfolio and build Value Propositions for the assigned products.<br><br>\r\n• Lead development of product marketing plan based on 4P methodology and implementation to achieve business targets.<br><br>\r\n• Lead the formulation and management of pricing, ensuring profitability for portfolio<br><br>\r\n• Provide market trends and competitors analysis.<br><br>\r\n• Work closely with supply chain team on sales forecasting and to ensure inventory management.<br><br>\r\n• Lead development of sales forecasting for the assigned products/categories.<br><br>\r\n• Track and monitor assigned products’ sales performance on a daily basis<br><br>\r\n• Lead team on day-to-day business operations.', '*  Good University degree/Master degree, preferably in Marketing, Business.<br><br>\r\n*  Related experience: at least 5 years work experience in relevant field<br><br>\r\n*  Excellent presentation skills with the ability to present to different levels of internal/external management/stakeholders.<br><br>\r\n*  Experience in Consumer Electronics / technology industry and/or technologically sDDAy.<br><br>\r\n*  SAP knowledge would be an advantage. ', '4970', 11, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/3363/samsung-electronics-squarelogo-1490601848974.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Samsung-Electronics-RVW13899392.htm'),
