(44, '226853', 'Investment Advisor', 'Standard Chartered Bank', 3.5, 3.5, 3, 3.3, 3.3, 3.3, 70, 'JOB PURPOSE : <br><br>\r\n* To provide overall Wealth Management product and services support to frontliners<br><br>\r\n*  To provide need-based advisory solution to customers<br><br>\r\n*  To participate in Wealth Management strategy in order to drive the overall Wealth Management sales and revenue with distribution team<br><br>\r\n*  To work closely with the Wealth product managers to ensure the success of the product-launched and seamless sales process<br><br>\r\n*  To work closely with the Wealth compliance manager for compliance with all regulations and controls set by the Bank and external regulatory authorities<br><br>\r\n*  To perform PCI roll-over duty for selected branches ', '* Strong leadership qualities, excellent with interpersonal skills and multinational awareness and sensitivity.<br><br>\r\n*  Effective oral and written communication skills, able to deal effectively with people at all levels (internal and external) and in difficult and complex situations.<br><br>\r\n*  Selling skills in wealth management products.<br><br>\r\n*  Relevant depth of experience in the industry.<br><br>\r\n*  Knowledge and understanding of products and services in strategic Asset Allocation.<br><br>\r\n*  Good understanding of relevant wealth management products and services.<br><br>\r\n*  Sound understanding of all business guidelines and compliance requirements and issues.<br><br>\r\n*  In-depth understanding of key business drivers in dedicated geographical market(s) with sound understanding of legal, political and economic situation/ framework.<br><br>\r\n*  Deep understanding of cultural, ethnic and religious market conditions.<br><br>\r\n*  Outstanding communication and presentation skills.<br><br>\r\n*  Focus, drive to lead, leading people, delivering results, endurance, personal perseverance, strong self motivation, entrepreneurial, team player.<br><br>\r\n*  Highly motivated and self-starter. Possess Business mindset.<br><br>\r\n*  Ability to analyze statistical data and extract information to identify trends and correlation.<br><br>\r\n*  Creative problem solving abilities.\r\n', '4970', 7, 'https://media.glassdoor.com/sqll/226853/standard-chartered-bank-squarelogo.png', 'http://www.glassdoor.com/Reviews/Employee-Review-Standard-Chartered-Bank-RVW8871850.htm');
